# Backend Environment Variables Template

Copy this to a `.env` file in the backend folder and update with your values.

## Server Configuration
PORT=5000

## Database Configuration
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/dms
# For MongoDB Atlas (cloud):
# MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/dms

## JWT Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key_change_in_production_12345
JWT_EXPIRE=7d

## File Upload Configuration
MAX_FILE_SIZE=10485760

## Frontend Configuration
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:4200

## Production Settings (if deploying)
# NODE_ENV=production
